description:
What values are logged to the console when this code runs?

for (let i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
  console.log(i);
}

What is the value of total after this code runs?

let total = 0;
for (let i = 1; i <= 4; i++) {
  total += i;
}

How many times does the loop body execute?

for (let i = 0; i < 9; i += 3) {
  // loop body
}

What is logged by this code?

const nums = [10, 20, 30];
for (let i = 0; i <= nums.length; i++) {
  console.log(nums[i]);
}

What is logged when this code runs?

for (let i = 0; i < 5; i++) {
  if (i === 3) break;
  console.log(i);
}

What is logged when this code runs?

for (let i = 0; i < 5; i++) {
  if (i % 2 === 0) continue;
  console.log(i);
}

How many times is 'x' logged?

for (let i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
  for (let j = 0; j < 4; j++) {
    console.log('x');
  }
}
